title: Wholesale Price of Bleached Muslin, 4-4, Fruit of the Loom Mills for United States
notes:
Reference Title To Series Changes In The Source From Time To Time. The Most Common Citations Are "Shirtings, Bleached, 4-4, Fruit Of The Loom" From The Approximate Dates 1890-1920 And "Muslin, Bleached, 4-4, Fruit Of The Loom" After 1920. Prices For 1890-1916 Are The First Price In The Month; Prices Quoted For 1917-1944 Are Monthly Average Prices. Source: Bls Bulletin No. 39, Pp. 370-371, Following Bulletins, And Monthly "Wholesale Price" Bulletins

This NBER data series m04084 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
